- The easiest way, install :
rvm
ruby 1.9.2
rubygem
rails
bundle
wkhtmltopdf :
	https://github.com/jdpace/PDFKit/wiki/Installing-WKHTMLTOPDF
	see config/initializers/pdfkit.rb
manage langage ... ?
heroku

- Then run into application home :
bundle install

- For testing purpose, run 
rake db:reset
rake db:populate
